<s> It already carries a strong whiff of anti-design ideology.  </s>
<s> "Resource" is surely better than page, though.  </s>
<s> You could have two or three links to a homepage using different forms.  </s>
<s> Besides, we often talk about alternatives in accessibility.  </s>
